Ba violences sexuelles emati motango mingi na monyele (est) ya ekolo Congo démocratique, eyebisi Médecins sans frontières (MSF). Koleka bato 560 bazalaki ba victimes na sanza misato. 
 "Na trimestre ya misato ya 2019, koleka ba majeures 476 mpe ba mineures 93 bazalaki ba victimes sexuelles na territoire ya Masisi na etuka ya Nord-Kivu," kolanda MSF.
"Na libandeli ya mobu, tozwaki mokumba ya koleka mbala mibale motango ya bato bazwi mpasi ya violences sexuelles na kotala oyo ya mobu moleki," eyebisi Ewald Stals, mokambi ya misala MSF na terrain, na zone ya santé ya Masisi.
"Wuto Janvier kino septembre, misala mya biso basalisi koleka bana 11.220 baliaka malamu te, ba victimes 2.310 ya violences sexuelles mpe bato bazoki na mbeli 1.980," elobi liyebisi.
Bomati ya motango boye bosalami likolo bozangi bokengi na Masisi, Rutshuru mpe Walikale, kolanda MSF.
ONG eye elobi ete mabe maye masalami mingi na baye bazali na bibundeli mpe na ba civils lokola.